"Compared to other European countries, Germany is lagging behind," explains VfB chairman Röttgermann.
Just falling into nostalgia and transfiguring the old times is no longer enough today.
The aim is to preserve the tradition of the association, but at the same time to align the company with the modern market.
"We live in a digitalized world," says Dutt.
